## Solution:

We have

$$
\begin{aligned}
& I_{n}=\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}}\left(e^{x} \tan x\right)^{n-1} e^{x}\left(1+\tan x+\tan^{2} x\right) d x=\ldots \ldots \ldots \\
