\end{aligned}
$$

Then \( n\left(\sqrt[n^{2}]{n I_{n}}-1\right)=n\left(e^{\frac{\pi}{4 n}}-1\right)=\frac{e^{\frac{\pi}{4 n}}-1}{\frac{\pi}{4 n}} \cdot \frac{\pi}{4} \)

Thus, the required limit is \(\frac{\pi}{4}\). \(\qquad\) (1p)

